![Episode9.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1575049058912-GWDL5RERSRTLS2YSV0UI/Episode9.jpg)

Another week and even more Issues! This week the guys at ComicBook Clique dissect Doomsday Clock #2 as the story of the Watchmen characters traveling to the DC Universe takes it up a notch! Ozy meets Lex, Rorschach meets Batman and ....is THAT who I THINK it is? AND HE'S ALIVE?! More surprises, insight and analysis than Dr. Manhattan can wrap a finger around as the guys take a deep dive into Doomsday Clock.

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
